darkness seize upon it; let it not be joined unto the days of the year, let it not come into the number of the months.","year":-1520},{"id":"recYlVofDlnTCgZa7","ref":"Job.3.7","text":"Lo, let that night be solitary, let no joyful voice come therein.","year":-1520},{"id":"recKLs9JOReMFEU7q","ref":"Job.3.8","text":"Let them curse it that curse the day, who are ready to raise up their mourning.","year":-1520}]}
